  {
    "content_id": 419397,
    "reference_id": 108996,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "1 Wathesalonike 5:1–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "52005001-52005011",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Hakuna anayejua Yesu atarudi lini duniani. Paulo aliuita wakati huo <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108571\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">siku ya Bwana</span>.</p><p>Kuelezea, Paulo alitumia maneno ya Yesu kuhusu maumivu ya uzazi na wezi usiku (Mathayo 24:8 na 43). Paulo alizungumza kuhusu kurudi kwa Yesu kama mwisho wa wakati wa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108039\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">giza</span> na usiku.</p><p>Pia alielezea kurudi kwa Yesu kama mwanzo wa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108546\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">nuru</span> na mchana. Paulo alitaka Wathesalonike kusubiri wakati huo kwa matumaini.</p><p>Matumaini yao lazima yawe imara na yawalinde kama kofia. Imani na upendo wao vilikuwa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108157\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">silaha za kiroho</span>.</p><p>Wathesalonike walipaswa kutiana moyo wao kwa wao kupitia tumaini lao, imani na upendo.</p>",
